(`presheafValue_isStronglyNoetherian_faithful`). Honest leaf.

**Established route (2026-06-09, after the plus/minus discharges).** The B-side overlap
datum (`(unitDatum P_B b).interSamePair (coUnitDatum P_B b)`) has `T = {1, b, b²}`,
