completion `presheafValue D'`.

Faithful reduction (reviewer (LL-bdd) Q-bdd-1) to the single external criterion
`isPowerBounded_of_forall_vle_one_spa_of_complete`: every Spa point `w` of `O_X(D')` pulls back
